{"about_the_game":"Input-based free-kick football game. No randomness, no scripting, only pure skill. <br>Score as many freekicks as you can while the AI goalkeeper and defenders try their best to stop you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">INPUT-BASED BALL TRAJECTORY</h2><br> Strike the ball at the correct position, and direction, with just enough power (and curve if necessary) to score. The ball trajectory is fully defined by your input only.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047000/extras/FreekickGif.gif?t=1732934032\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Intelligent AI goalkeepers and defenders.</h2><br>Your opponents will do the best they can to stop you from scoring. When you shoot, they will assert the trajectory to decide where, when, and how to intercept.<br>The goalkeeper moves to a good position before reaching for the ball just in time to stop a goal:<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047000/extras/GifProject.gif?t=1732934032\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A big stadium with thousands of fans cheering.</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047000/extras/ScreenshotStadiumOverview.png?t=1732934032\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">32 national teams' football kits.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Realistic goal-net physics.</h2><br>The net will react realistically to the ball.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047000/extras/ScreenshotStadiumGoalNet_-_Copy.png?t=1732934032\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Compete with your friends and other players on Steam Leaderboards.</h2>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047000/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732934032","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047000/page.bg.jpg?t=1732934032","capsule_image":"https://shared.aka